headline.main: W. Virginia Women Upset No. 19 Oklahoma in Big 12 Tournament
headline.print_headline: W. Virginia Women Upset No. 19 Oklahoma in Big 12 Tournament

lead_paragraph: Tynice Martin scored 21 points, Teana Muldrow added 19 with eight rebounds and West Virginia beat No. 19 Oklahoma 82-58 in the Big 12 Conference Tournament on Saturday night.
